<p>Asher showed off her taut torso and trim pins as she later cooled off in the water solo. </p>

<p>The Australian beauty relocated to the NSW coastal town in order to film her upcoming TV series, Nine Perfect Strangers. </p>

<p>However, her husband Vincent Fantauzzo, is stuck in lockdown in the couple's hometown of Melbourne as a result of the COVID-19 pandemic. </p>

